# @desc   From the Inbox tab, open the first chat/report in the LHN. Triggers the ManualOpenReport Sentry span (LHN row press -> report screen mounted with composer visible). Assumes the user is signed in with at least one chat in the Inbox.
# @pre    text="Inbox"
# @post   role="textview" label="Write something..."
# @tag    chat
# @tag    navigation
# @tag    perf
